PocService Service that provides access to POC specific functionality.

PocURIFactory

Example:
PortletActionPocService Version of the PortletPocService that allows to modify the current navigational state during the action phase of the portlet.
PortletEventPocService Version of the PortletPocService that allows to modify the current navigational state during the event phase of the portlet.
PortletMimePocService Version of the PortletPocService that can be used in a render or resource request of a JSR286 compatible portlet.
PortletPocService Portlet version of the PocService that is associated with one portlet window.

PortletRenderPocService Version of the PortletPocService that can be used in a render request of a JSR286 compatible portlet.
PortletResourcePocService Version of the PortletPocService that can be used in a resource request of a JSR286 compatible portlet.
